				\begin{document}$${\text{Chlorophyll}} \,a\,\left( {{\text{mg L}}^{ - 1} } \right) = 13.43 \, \times {\text{ OD}}_{665}$$\end{document}Chlorophyllamg L-1=13.43×OD665
